{"tid":2161041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致泛民/本土派：","createTime":"2020-08-17T10:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T11:14:36.000Z","uid":60644,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7194d872cc952862417678892021c853f13c8110","tid":2161041,"uid":60644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:33:52.000Z","msg":"成為人大委任議員心情如何<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FScXMFP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFScXMFP.png&h=2b43dcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Jyv6FT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Jyv6FT.jpg&h=2ea99557&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"196ea5211e1eee4be185bb4732999b1fee6a2645","tid":2161041,"uid":254183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:42:15.000Z","msg":"中國八大民主黨派：「我唔坐住個位咪益左共產黨？」<br />\n<br />\n唔知咩叫八大民主政黨去 google，佢地就係諸君既未來。你估共產黨第一日應付你班選舉政棍？人地一早睇穿保你唔使選都有個席，就會自己仆住去。"},{"pid":"28f5da612bdc7049300aad4b8b4bac55e14f6ea4","tid":2161041,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:46:41.000Z","msg":"花你一分鐘填email加入香港民研收問卷  反對泛民違憲廷任<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2161048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2161048</a>"},{"pid":"16230bb66bbbb4811ccf7351d35e1c080ead61e1","tid":2161041,"uid":60644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"畀你留多一年，一年後睇下仲有冇人去投票畀你地<br />\n<br />\n殺雞取卵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6851b625a2e652b2d971e8bf6055f9794f5f9b","tid":2161041,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:14:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">邊條食屎狗要非法廷任，<br />\n直接支持人大獨裁決定，<br />\n忽視香港人民選舉公義！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">唔好再自稱民主派！</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講最錯係港共<br />\n港共係人所皆知嘅狗屎垃圾殺人犯<br />\n但唔代表佢迫你就要做！<br />\n<br />\n有個強姦犯姦泛民老母<br />\n之後佢叫泛民姦埋一份<br />\n唔係就要切咗泛民碌嘢<br />\n後泛民主流決定姦老母<br />\n<br />\n泛民算咩嘢受害者？<br />\n<br />\n家陣就係要否定港共，泛民係唔係痴咗線<br />\n佢委任你都死去做，即係認同佢推遲選舉<br />\n認同立會可以再用委任，再認同人大授權<br />\n<br />\n以上加埋有咩嘢後果？"}]}